{"tid":868365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狠嗆Switch一把，華為自豪Mate 20 X螢幕更大、續航力更強","createTime":"2018-10-19T11:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:32:53.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"dadb88c6b5096bf0369a6a5cc2ccdd06ab9bdc24","tid":868365,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/1810/18-huawei-07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F1810%2F18-huawei-07.jpg&h=8bfe9e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒想到 Switch 也有被狠嗆的一天。中國手機商華為（Huawei Mobile）17 日在倫敦舉辦新機發表會；席間，Nintendo Switch 被狠嗆螢幕尺寸，續航力、解析度各個都不如人，現成了輿論焦點。<br />\n<br />\n華為這場 17 日在倫敦舉辦的新機發表會，對全新 Mate 20 系列賦予不小期望。<br />\n<br />\n發表會末端以 Mate 20 X 為主角，強調支援 Dolby Atmos 的雙立體聲超低音喇叭，帶來優於 iPhone Xs Max 的 120% 強勁低音能力。<br />\n<br />\n其他像是運作一個小時遊戲 App 後，Mate 20 X 可以低於 Samsung Galaxy Note 9 和 iPhone X 的機身溫度。<br />\n<br />\n重點來了，華為公開一組 Mate 20 X 適用的遊戲控制器周邊，強調 Mate 20 X 比 Nintendo Switch 具備更大的螢幕、雙倍電池續航力，以及 1080p 更高的螢幕解析度（Switch 在掌機模式的解析度是 720p）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/1810/18-huawei-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F1810%2F18-huawei-01.jpg&h=4d9197f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/TangBao/1810/18-huawei-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FTangBao%2F1810%2F18-huawei-03.jpg&h=0fb4908b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個比較是很有趣的，Nintendo Switch 硬體強度確實每個都輸給 Mate 20 X。但是任天堂持有的遊戲 IP 資源卻是華為沒有的。<br />\n<br />\n是說，再比下去的話......Switch 的歐洲官方售價 280 歐元，只有 Mate 20 X 售價 899 歐元的....1/3 都不到；糟了，Switch 連價格都輸了。<br />\n<br />\n全程發表會影片如下，Nintendo Switch 的登場約自 1:22:43 開始。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FzYJNZT2Ico?t=4963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFzYJNZT2Ico%3Ft%3D4963&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=2b260729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FzYJNZT2Ico?t=4963</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/36778/huawei-says-mate-20-x-is-better-than-nintendo-switch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F36778%2Fhuawei-says-mate-20-x-is-better-than-nintendo-switch&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=beae4d01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/36778/huawei-says-mate-20-x-is-better-than-nintendo-switch</a><br />\n<br />\n拎部8000蚊嘅手機同部2XXX蚊嘅console比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718060bf1c1714d96b9674fe77dcb642027f4531","tid":868365,"uid":2404,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"係咪傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f71a10a5353f8d4de9cd59f7f3a61c50c6a17f","tid":868365,"uid":31215,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"唔好同3DS比<br />\n仲贏得勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03ff2212461b701b545b29b93865d40a1517660","tid":868365,"uid":105678,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"支持祖國打倒日本，買華為貨 !<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;發自Iphone XS MAX"},{"pid":"cd2a4b8e210c8fb473ce6006e288e04b73ed2aeb","tid":868365,"uid":121146,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"咪又係玩埋d課金game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d310635da6e072abcc9939a80c5009e386078159","tid":868365,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7dbf68025f4b